OL,4,Cdaughter's birth 'could have been
OL,5,Csaved'
OL,7,FITV Granada Reports correspondent Ann
OL,8,FO'Connor was at the inquest into
OL,9,FThomas' death.
OL,11,FA dad-to-be who died on the day of his
OL,12,Fdaughter's birth may have lived to
OL,13,Fmeet her had a heart defect not been
OL,14,Fmissed, a coroner has ruled.
OL,16,FThomas Gibson was 40 when his partner
OL,17,FRebecca Moss tried to wake him at
OL,18,Ftheir home in on 7 June 2023, as she
OL,19,Fgot ready to go to hospital for an
OL,20,Felective caesarean.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
