OL,3,CDad-to-be who died on day of
OL,4,Cdaughter's birth 'could have been
OL,5,Csaved'
OL,7,FShe said to him: "Wake up, it's baby
OL,8,Fday."
OL,10,FWhen he didn't respond, she went to
OL,11,Fkiss him but found him stiff and cold.
OL,13,FRebecca performed emergency first aid
OL,14,Funtil an ambulance arrived, but he was
OL,15,Fdeclared by medics once they arrived.
OL,17,FLater that day, she gave birth to
OL,18,Ftheir daughter Harper.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
