OL,3,CDad-to-be who died on day of
OL,4,Cdaughter's birth 'could have been
OL,5,Csaved'
OL,7,FAn inquest has now concluded that
OL,8,FThomas' death could have been
OL,9,Fprevented, as an ECG scan 11 days
OL,10,Fbeforehand had shown him "to be
OL,11,Fexperiencing complete heart block".
OL,13,FHowever, medics at hospital failed to
OL,14,F"appreciate" this and did not provide
OL,15,Fany treatment.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
