OL,3,CDad-to-be who died on day of
OL,4,Cdaughter's birth 'could have been
OL,5,Csaved'
OL,7,FCoroner Christopher Morris said: "Had
OL,8,Fthis been appreciated Mr Gibson would
OL,9,Fhave been admitted under the care of
OL,10,Fcardiologists, a series of
OL,11,Finvestigations undertaken, which would
OL,12,Fprobably have culminated in an
OL,13,Fimplantable device, such as a
OL,14,Fpacemaker being fitted.
OL,16,F"It is likely these measures would
OL,17,Fhave avoided his death."
