OL,5,Csaved'
OL,7,FDr Ainsley replied: "I think the short
OL,8,Fduration between the ECG and his heart
OL,9,Fgiving way, I think it's more than
OL,10,Flikely he would have avoided his
OL,11,Fdeath."
OL,13,FThe inquest heard that Thomas worked
OL,14,Fin a timber yard and was physically
OL,15,Ffit but had been suffering from a
OL,16,Fstomach bug, including cramps and
OL,17,Fdiarrhoea, for around three weeks
OL,18,Fbefore his death.
