OL,7,FOn 27 May 2023, Thomas went to
OL,8,FWythenshawe Hospital's A&E department
OL,9,Fand received an ECG scan.
OL,11,FHe was seen by Dr Oliver Handley, who
OL,12,Frecognised that his ECG trace showed
OL,13,Fsigns of an abnormality and referred
OL,14,Fit to a more senior medic, Dr Thomas
OL,15,FBull, the medical registrar, for a
OL,16,Fsecond opinion.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
