OL,3,CDad-to-be who died on day of
OL,4,Cdaughter's birth 'could have been
OL,5,Csaved'
OL,7,FDr Bull said the ECG scan was likely
OL,8,Fto represent an abnormality he
OL,9,Fdescribed as an intraventricular
OL,10,Fblock, which is "not an uncommon
OL,11,Ffinding" and not clinically
OL,12,F"significant" without other heart-
OL,13,Frelated symptoms.
OL,15,FAs there were no other heart-related
OL,16,Fsymptoms he was discharged.
OL,18,FBut later analysis concluded that the
OL,19,FECG identified a complete heart block,
OL,20,Falso known as a third-degree heart
OL,21,Fblock, the most serious kind.
