OL,7,FDr Matthew Thornber, a consultant at
OL,8,Fthe hospital, said the two ECGs taken
OL,9,Fwere not "textbook" examples of
OL,10,Flooking like a heart block condition
OL,11,Fand such diagnosis requires nuance and
OL,12,Fexperience.
OL,14,F"This is not a barn door easy miss,"
OL,15,Fhe said.
