OL,7,FThe coroner said he would be writing a
OL,8,Fprevention of future deaths report,
OL,9,Faddressed to the chief executive of
OL,10,Fthe Manchester University NHS
OL,11,FFoundation Trust and the National
OL,12,FInstitute of Clinical Excellence
OL,13,Fconcerning clinical practice around
OL,14,Fthe interpretation of ECG scans.
