OL,7,FMiss Toli Onon, Joint Group Chief
OL,8,FMedical Officer at Manchester
OL,9,FUniversity NHS Foundation Trust, said:
OL,10,F"We wish again to extend our
OL,11,Fcondolences and sincere sympathies to
OL,12,FMr Gibson's family at this very
OL,13,Fdifficult time.
OL,15,F"The Trust has undertaken a thorough
OL,16,Finvestigation to examine the
OL,17,Fcircumstances following Mr Gibson's
OL,18,Fvery sad death, and we apologise for
OL,19,Fwhere our care has fallen short of the
OL,20,Fhigh standards to which we aspire.
