OL,9,Fand we will be reviewing the Coroner's
OL,10,Fconclusion carefully, to ensure
OL,11,Ffurther learning for the Trust is
OL,12,Faddressed and applied to our constant
OL,13,Fwork to improve our patients' safety,
OL,14,Fquality of care, and experience."
